data.text:
If you have a concern regarding a child or young person, please contact the Children's Services Front Door who ensure that children, young people and their families receive the correct support when needs are identified and at the most appropriate level.

The team supports other practitioners by advising them of the correct route for support to families and children. The focus is to make safe decisions about children at the earliest opportunity.
